title: Converse CONS Project: London Artists on Inspiration
description:
We asked London based illustrator Sam Taylor to curate a tight crew of artists to transform the CONS Project space in London. Inspiration was everywhere, from the local characters of Peckham to the space itself.

For the full line-up and to apply for tickets to all CONS Project London events head to http://conversecons.com/ldn
